      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span id="more-127"></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 30pt; color: white;">RATING:</span> <img src='http://levelingguidesforwow.com/wp-content/plugins/rate-my-stuff/rating_star.solid.gif' alt='world of warcraft'/><img src='http://levelingguidesforwow.com/wp-content/plugins/rate-my-stuff/rating_star.solid.gif' alt='world of warcraft'/><img src='http://levelingguidesforwow.com/wp-content/plugins/rate-my-stuff/rating_star.solid.gif' alt='world of warcraft'/><img src='http://levelingguidesforwow.com/wp-content/plugins/rate-my-stuff/rating_star.solid.gif' alt='world of warcraft'/><img src='http://levelingguidesforwow.com/wp-content/plugins/rate-my-stuff/rating_star.empty.gif' alt='world of warcraft power leveling guides'/></p>
<p>About <a rel="nofollow" href="http://levelingguidesforwow.com/recommended/KGDruid">Druid Leveling Guide by Killer Guides</a>:</p>
<blockquote><p><a rel="nofollow" href="http://levelingguidesforwow.com/recommended/KGDruid"><img src="http://levelingguidesforwow.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/09/world-of-warcraft-druid-guide-kg.jpg" alt="" title="world-of-warcraft-druid-guide-kg" width="180" height="230" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-128" align="left" style="margin: 10px;" /></a>  As with all of the guides at <strong>KillerGuides</strong>, their <strong>WoW Druid Leveling Guide</strong> is top notch.  </p>
<p>This guide was written and put together by Scott Campbell, who has been playing World of Warcraft since 2004, is a member of one of the top raiding guilds and has written other successful guides on Warcraft and other MMORPG.</p>
<p><a rel="nofollow" href="http://levelingguidesforwow.com/recommended/KGDruid">KillerGuides <strong>Druid Guide</strong></a> is designed to show you exactly how the top raid and PvP druids do their thing.  Some of the things you&#8217;ll learn in this guide will be:</p>
<p>- How to reach level 70 with your druid in 10 days<br />
The leveling guide goes into the the details of what you need level by level.  It lists quests, which mobs you should be hunting, where to find those mobs and many more.  In addition to that, the guide also doesn&#8217;t restrict itself to solo game play as it also provides an advanced guide for grouping. </p>
<p>- How to succeed in end level raids with druid specific strategies for raid encounters<br />
You&#8217;ll find out what talent druid build options you should be using to maximize your raids, where to get the right equipment and how to handle certain boss mobs.  </p>
<p>- You will learn talent builds in a way no one has shared before<br />
This information comes from actual game data that was collected over massive amounts of playing time and it comes from the perspective of professional raiders.  Learn the efficiency of restoration, balance and feral trees in regards to solo, group, raid and PvP encounters.</p>
<p>- How to become a guru on druid equipment<br />
This takes you from the beginning as a newbie to the end with solid gear strategy.  Lists easily obtained blue items, deadly feral gear, poison resist and more.  It even shows you the best choice of weapons for each level.</p>
<p>Other things this guide covers in detail:</p>
<p>- Discover 10 different secret <strong>gold making methods</strong> for druids<br />
- Druid Skills, Stats and Spells<br />
- Step by Step Druid Quests<br />
- PvP Strategies for Druids<br />
- Macros and Add-ons for Druids<br />
- Free updates and more<br />
You can learn more about this Druid Guide at the official site:<br />
<a rel="nofollow" href="http://levelingguidesforwow.com/recommended/KGDruid">Druid Leveling Guide by Killer Guides</a>
</p></blockquote>
<p>Some ACTUAL <a rel="nofollow" href="http://levelingguidesforwow.com/recommended/KGDruid">Druid Leveling Guide by Killer Guides</a> User Feedback:</p>
<blockquote><p>
&#8220;The best part about this guide is the combat strategies.&#8221;<br />
- WoW-Strategy.com</p>
<p>&#8220;If the Druid is already your favorite character class, you will love it even more once you become a better player.&#8221;<br />
- WoWPlayersGuides.com
</p></blockquote>
<p>Overall and Final Comments:</p>
<blockquote><p>
This guide is really strong when it comes to playing the druid character.  It does have other aspects of World of Warcraft play that aren&#8217;t druid specific, these areas are nowhere near as detailed as the druid aspects.  Which is good as this is a druid guide and it&#8217;s strength should lie in the information, strategies, tips and techniques that will help you with your druid game play&#8230;.</p>
<p>It does that very well!!
</p></blockquote>
