<p>About the only cons you&#8217;ll find with this guide is that it&#8217;s solely an Alliance Leveling guide and it doesn&#8217;t include videos like Joana&#8217;s leveling guide.  Other than that, this is one of the top leveling guides you&#8217;ll find for World of Warcraft.
